text.section:
"Mineral" includes:
Gas;
Oil and oil shale;
Coal;
Gaseous, liquid, and solid hydrocarbons;
Cement materials, sand and gravel, road materials, and building stone;
Chemical substances;
Gemstone, metallic, fissionable, and nonfissionable ores; and
Colloidal and other clay, steam, and geothermal resources.
